{
  "stem": "7506.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember being aware that people would sit around the radio listening to the news and that there was fighting.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES] Now I probably would imagine it was in Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that's the only change that I remember, really and truly, at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was, of course, before Holland was occupied.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not before the war so much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, of course, once that Holland was occupied, I noticed changes in the-- in the house, because of my parents talking about people that had left, that had gotten out, that had been able to pay to get out, to get on fishing boats across the North Sea to get-- to get to England.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people had gone to Switzerland, [PAUSES] who knew the right people or were able to pay the right people the amounts required to get out and leave Holland.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Around that time, of course, when those things were happening, I was aware that things were changing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I remember the occupation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember the Germans arriving very near to where I lived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES] I remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, of course, slowly I remembered that I was told that there had been, in different parts of Amsterdam, what they call razzias, where the Germans would block off streets, where you couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never-- I never experienced that personally.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They'd block off the streets, and everybody that was in there would have to be showing their papers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course, at that time, as the occupation progressed, we had to wear a star.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The yellow star.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Where my grandparents lived, they had to put up boards at certain streets, saying Judenviertel, in Dutch-- in German, and Joodevijk, which is-- that's Dutch translation.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES] And we all wore the star.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What's that?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, Judenviertel means Jewish quarter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jewish area.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
